dct_description_sm: This point data represents address points for Milwaukee County in 2018. The dataset was originally published by the Milwuakee County Land Information Office in 2017. The dataset was last updated in 2018. [points representing locations of addresses - points are placed within the parcel with which the address is assocated - when possible, points are placed within the footprint of the building with which the address is associated - when a parcel or building is associated with multiple addresses, multiple points will be placed per parcel or building]
